      <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-dark mb-3 mt-6">CIPD 5CO02 Assignment Example (Evidence-based Practice)</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">CIPD 5CO02 also known as evidence-based practice covers the importance of having qualitative and quantitative information when making important decisions. This unit seeks to develop ethical reasoning in evidence analysis and quantifying value in people's practice. CIPD 5CO02 Assignment Example</p>
