      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">If you have just joined the HR profession, this is the basic level and it will lay your foundation in your career. Surely, you need a good starting footing to encourage you to keep going on the subsequent levels; therefore, you need to consider CIPD assignment help.</p>
